        <name>
            <text>13.3.2.2a Area under a curve</text>
        </name>
        <questiontext format="html">
            <text><![CDATA[
<p class="HELM_exercise">
    <span class="multilang" lang="en">
        Exercise
    </span>
    <span class="multilang" lang="no">
        Oppgave
    </span>
</p>
<p>
    <span class="multilang" lang="en">
        In each question you should check that the required area lies entirely above the horizontal axis.
    </span>
    <span class="multilang" lang="no">
        Husk &#229; sjekke at omr&#229;det du skal finne faktisk ligger over horisontalaksen.
    </span>
</p>
<br/>
<ol class="HELM_parts">
    <li>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            Find the area under the curve \(y={@exp1@}\) and above the x-axis between \(x = {@l1@}\) and \(x = {@u1@}\).
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Finn arealet under kurven \(y={@exp1@}\) og over x-aksen mellom \(x = {@l1@}\) og \(x = {@u1@}\).
        </span>
        [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]] [[feedback:prt1]]
    </li>
    <li>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            Find the area under the curve \(y={@exp2@}\) and the x-axis between \(x = {@l2@}\) and \(x = {@u2@}\).
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Finn arealet avgrenset av kurven \(y={@exp2@}\) og x-aksen mellom \(x = {@l2@}\) og \(x = {@u2@}\).
        </span>
        [[input:ans2]] [[validation:ans2]] [[feedback:prt2]]
    </li>
</ol>
]]></text>
