        <generalfeedback format="html">
            <text><![CDATA[
<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;">
</p>
<p>
    <span class="multilang" lang="en">
        Since the required area lies entirely above the horizontal axis for each question, the area under the curve \(y\) between \(x = a\) and \(x = b\) is \(\int_{a}^{b} y(x) \, dx\).
    </span>
    <span class="multilang" lang="no">
        Siden omr&#229;det i begge oppgavene ligger over horisontalaksen, er arealet under kurven \(y\) mellom \(x = a\) og \(x = b\) gitt ved \(\int_{a}^{b} y(x) \, dx\).
    </span>
</p>
<br/>
<ol>
    <li>
        \(\displaystyle \int_{@l1@}^{@u1@}{@exp1@}\, dx = \left[ {@int(exp1,x)@} \right]_{@l1@}^{@u1@} = {@ta1@}\).
    </li>
    <li>
        \(\displaystyle \int_{@l2@}^{@u2@}{@exp2@}\, dx =&#160;\left[ {@int(exp2,x)@} \right]_{@l2@}^{@u2@} = {@ta2@}\).
    </li>
</ol>
<br/>
<p>
</p>
